Package: citec
Title: Scrapes data from CitEc citation database
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Aboozar", "Hadavand", email = "hadavand.a@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Scrapes and downloads citation data from CitEc. CitEc is a RePEc service providing citation data for Economics. 
